dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Carneros Rocks and Belridge quadrangles, San Luis Obispo and Kern counties, California
dct_alternative_sm: Geology Carneros Rocks and Belridge quadrangles
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights.

"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Carneros Rocks, CA 1959, photorevised 1982, DMA 2054 IV NE -- Series V895; Belridge, CA 1953, photorevised 1973, AMS 2054 I NW --Series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
